<snippet>
	<content><![CDATA[const initialize2DArray = (w, h, val = null) =>
  Array(h)
    .fill()
    .map(() => Array(w).fill(val));]]></content>
	<description>Initializes a 2D array of given width and height and value.  Use `Array.map()` to generate h rows where each is a new array of size w initialize with value. If the value is not provided, default to `null`.</description>
